file_content.text: My lord, what are you doing? You can't do this to me! I love you!
What are you waiting for? Use the dream-rock.
I'm ready if you are, Gormak. This is the nightmare.
It's time for you to bleed, ghost. Use the dream-rock, Gormak.
I am trying. Corruption is strong here. Hard to fight.
What's the matter? Lost your sense of humor? You won't beat me that easily.
My lord! You came back! I missed you so much.
Why did you leave me? Why did you leave me here to die?
Why did you leave me? Why did you leave me all alone?
